Kiyovu Sports vs Mukura Victory Sports

Kiyovu Sports 0-1 Mukura Victory Sports

Uko umukino uri kugenda

Umwanditsi

: Eric Tony Ukurikiyimfura

Amafoto

: Ntare Julius

16:56

Kiyovu Sports isezereye Mukura ifite igikombe giheruka

N'ubwo Mukura Victory Sports itsinze igitego 1-0 mu mukino wo kwishyura, isezerewe na Kiyovu Sports ku bitego 3-2 mu mikino yombi kuko yari yatsindiwe mu rugo ibitego 3-1.

Mukura ni yo yatwaye igikombe cy'Amahoro mu mwaka ushize wa 2018.

Mu yindi mikino yabaye, Intare FC zatsinze Bugesera FC ibitego 2-1, ziyisezerera ku bitego 4-2. Gicumbi yanganyije na Espoir FC i Rusizi igitego 1-1, ikipe yo mu mayaruguru irakomeza kuko umukino ubanza wari warangiye ari 0-0. Police FC yasezereye Etoile de l'Est ku bitego 3-2 mu mikino yombi nyuma yo kunganya igitego 1-1 uyu munsi.





Tubashimire mwese twabanye kuri uyu mukino. Tuzasubire Ejo ku Cyumweru hari imikino yindi ya 1/8 yo kwishyura.

16:53

Ikaze kuri Stade Mumena

IGIHE ibahaye ikaze kuri Stade de l'Amitie izwi nka Stade Mumena. Hagiye kubera umukino wo kwishyura wa 1/8 cy'Igikombe cy'Amahoro hagati ya Kiyovu Sports na Mukura Victory Sports guhera saa 15:00.

Mu mukino ubanza wabereye i Huye, ikipe ifite igikombe giheruka yatsindiwe iwayo ibitego 3-1.
